                                                                                             The resulting GRANT results for the specified policy are below:
                                                                                                                               Table 3: Result of GRANT Testing
                                                                                                                     Section of Policy       cc   lo   mc   mr     oc   pc
                                                                                                                     !mr & !oc & mc          0    0    1    0      0    0
                                                                                                                     cc & lo                 1    1    0    0      0    0
